name: dataproc_projects_regions_jobs_delete
description: Deletes the job from the project. If the job is active, the delete fails, and the response returns FAILED_PRECONDITION.

projectId.description: Required. The ID of the Google Cloud Platform project that the job belongs to.

region.description: Required. The Dataproc region in which to handle the request.
